OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright day for most,
OL,6,Fwith the best of the sunshine in the
OL,7,Feast. The cloud in the west may be
OL,8,Fthick enough at times for some patchy
OL,9,Frain, though more likely later in the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA short period of patchy rain
OL,13,Fspreading eastwards through the
OL,14,Fevening, though dry again overnight
OL,15,Fwith plenty of clear spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping. Turning chilly as winds
OL,17,Fremain light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
